{"talk":{"id":1881,"name":"Toby Eccles: Invest in social change","description":"Here's a stat worth knowing: In the UK, 63% of men who finish short-term prison sentences are back inside within a year for another crime. Helping them stay outside involves job training, classes, therapy. And it would pay off handsomely -- but the government can't find the funds. Toby Eccles shares an imaginative idea for how to change that:\u00a0the Social Impact Bond. It's an unusual bond that helps fund initiatives with a social goal through private money -- with the government paying back the investors (with interest) if the initiatives work.","slug":"toby_eccles_invest_in_social_change","recorded_at":"2013-06-12 00:00:00","published_at":"2013-12-02 15:59:50","updated_at":"2020-09-28 21:46:29","viewed_count":962066,"emailed_count":179,"event":{"id":241,"name":"TEDGlobal 2013"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2d8322e01cdb1b5d20c3a19efe1a37af869aeae4_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2d8322e01cdb1b5d20c3a19efe1a37af869aeae4_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2d8322e01cdb1b5d20c3a19efe1a37af869aeae4_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"1600x1200","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2d8322e01cdb1b5d20c3a19efe1a37af869aeae4_1600x1200.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":false,"media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/TobyEccles_2013G-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":4964651,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/TobyEccles_2013G-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":13686195,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/TobyEccles_2013G-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":24302361,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"450k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.